docs/*
!docs/whitepaper.md
!docs/whitepaper.html
!docs/whitepaper.pdf
!docs/whitepaper_full.md
!docs/whitepaper_full.html
!docs/whitepaper_full.pdf
# --- arXiv LaTeX package (source + figures + compiled pdf) ---
!docs/arxiv/
docs/arxiv/*.tar.gz

# --- scratch ---
*.log
*.tmp
scratchpad/

!docs/gelo.md
!docs/whitepaper2.md

